Dear All
Moving to Beersheva on November 22, 2017 with wife as postdoc in university. A small apt with facilities with walking distance to the university and train station will be excellent. Ground or 1st floor preferable. Thanks in advance.

apartment is available : suitable for two persons or family, 5 mins walking from Technion Nesher gate. 2 Bed rooms, 1 big living room, 1 big kitchen, 1 washroom. very pleasant view from the apartment.
available for rent/sublet from Nov 2017 to Aug 2018.
Address : Darech HaTechnion 48, Nesher.
Furniture and Appliance: fridge, washing machine, microwave, gas oven with grill, geyser, dining table, sofa, double bed, two large wardrobe, Chairs, Air conditioning in every room.
Rent : 2500 NIS per month + Arnona (Tax) + electricity, water, gas bill extra
Contact Person: Kasinath : 0584701898
Susanta: 0584997883
email : kasi_chemistry@yahoo.com
susanta.chem@gmail.com
If anyone interested please let me know.

Last room left!
The apartment is for 3 partners in total. It is about 80 square meters and is located within walking distance of the train north of the university and the pubs "Manzila", "Coca" and so on ... The apartment has all the equipment required for a student.
In each room: closet, bed, mattress, study table and chair.
In the common space: living room, living room table, 32-inch television, refrigerator, microwave, toaster, electric hob, dining table and household utensils.
The apartment is located in a student area where there is also a supermarket and kiosk.
The price per room is 1000 NIS
For details please send a message or call 0524601230
evacuation in 1.10
*The ad was registered in English because 2 students from
Serbia live in the apartment and are looking for a third
partner.
*The ad addresses both Israelis and non-Israelis who studying
at the university.
